{"tid":1590930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【COM’ON】P牌仔有啲嘢想講","createTime":"2019-09-24T03:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T00:43:32.000Z","uid":320467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2f871de7ef13168e212456d8579e2836f3a2ce56","tid":1590930,"uid":320467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:01:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我知係P牌仔 但當香港真係病咗100日<br />\n真係好想為香港做啲嘢 各位幫手推吓得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n掙扎咗好耐 作為社工學生又無錢 但又無勇氣上前線<br />\n但一直以嚟真係好想為香港呢個家做啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n經過咗 612 721 811 831<br />\n烈士犧牲 太子站「被消失」 義士 <br />\n莫須有嘅罪名越嚟越多 好多popo情緒完全失控<br />\n再睇到呢幾日 Yellow Object 嘅言論 好多人都真心燥底<br />\n睇到身邊好多人都屈得好辛苦<br />\n甚至同屋企人好朋友都有好大分歧<br />\n<br />\n係呢段咁艱難嘅時期 真係好需要身邊人嘅幫助<br />\n身邊都有好多人已經開始頂唔順<br />\n發覺好似好難搵到個信任嘅人，願意聽吓自己講！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">COM&rsquo;ON </span></span></strong>係一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">匿名 TG </span></span>個人分享平台，由幾個志同道合社工學生自發成立<br />\n希望能夠為大家提供多一個渠道去分享自己的感受<br />\n無論大小事只要你／妳想講，有煩惱、唔開心，又或者單純想搵人傾吓分享吓<br />\n都可以試下搵我哋！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">唔洗提供任何個人資料</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">所有資料同對話內容，將不記名方式及絕對保密，不篤灰、不割席。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Telegram: comonhk<br />\nEmail: comonhk@gmail.com</span><br />\n俾個機會我哋同大家傾吓計！</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果你身邊有咩人有需要 都可以叫佢地搵吓我哋</strong><br />\n利申：我哋唔代表咩機構，只係幾個社工學生自發好想為呢場運動付出到可以付出嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaogvjV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaogvjV.jpg&h=c2c4cc55&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Credit: 由於時間同人手關係 圖改自 Freepik</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">期望約定大家煲底除罩相見<br />\n香港人，一個都不能少！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會 / 2389 2222 / touch@sbhk.org.hk / 24小時 / 廣東話<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會24小時多語服務 / 2896 0000 / jo@samaritans.org.hk / 24小時 / 廣東話<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線 / 2382 0000 / admin@sps.org.hk / 24小時 / 廣東話<br />\n<br />\n向晴熱線 / 18288 / fcsc@cfcsc.org.hk / 24小時 / 廣東話<br />\n<br />\n利民會「即時通」熱線 35122626 (24小時真人接聽)<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園 / 18281 / ceasecrisis@tungwahcsd.org / 24小時/ 廣東話﹑英語及普通話<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=0c9fdbdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a> (Website) / 91 012 012 (只限SMS) / hkopenup (WeChat / Facebook Page / Instagram) / info@openup.hk /24小時/  中文(廣東話、普通話)、英文</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6445a8e292de21309c73b5e6018812bef9d12d37","tid":1590930,"uid":320467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">P牌推唔到 大家幫幫忙 </span>"},{"pid":"c2d38c7b6425804bde213dd66dcb968624833357","tid":1590930,"uid":320467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">P牌推唔到 大家幫幫忙</span>"},{"pid":"e2725abaeb44a0d72bfe11f8675b54d86f96d701","tid":1590930,"uid":320467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:02:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">P牌推唔到 大家幫幫忙</span>"},{"pid":"57ca240b1224287355e0